I won’t say I did it in one day 🙃

The hardest part was getting started! The first step was to take everything out of the closet. I mean it… EVERYTHING! Laying it on the floor and not knowing where to begin was the hardest part, I even thought about putting everything back in as it was before 😂
Once I got the baskets in place, it was all about categorizing and decluttering.

If you find it as satisfying as I do we can probably be friends 😆

SAVE for when you’re ready to do yours! Just don’t think about it!

#closetorganization #organization #homeorganization #satisfyingvideos

14 years ago…

I met him and said yes without knowing he would be the best dad and husband I could have asked for. Thank you for all you do and for loving us the way only you can. We celebrate you today, but we’re thankful for you every single day. We love you babe. Wishing you a year full of blessings!
Life lately 🫶

The last picture 🥹😂
Momentos en los que todo lo demás se olvida because you realize you’re so in love with them and can’t stop taking pictures even if you’re running late to pick up your husband 😂🥴

When a stranger stops and asks if you want her to take a picture of us, ends up doing a mini shoot and then tells you she’s a photographer lol I’ll take it since I’m always behind the camera ☺️ On another note how big is she?! 🥹 My babies are getting so big and I’m one proud mama!
Feeling a little extra thankful and grateful for this girl of mine. Nothing makes my heart happier than to watch her enjoy herself and that’s exactly what I did.

9 years since I was blessed with the most amazing, beautiful, and good hearted girl. Happy birthday my sweet baby wishing you not just a great day but a beautiful life. To always be true to yourself, to learn, to grow, to have fun, enjoy life, to find your peace, your happiness…always. Love you to infinity and beyond 🤍

This was the end of her night 😂 En lo que le gusta hahaha De corazón muchas gracias por todo el cariño hacia ella hoy desde llamadas, mensajes, posts, anything, and everything. Specially pasar tiempo con ella. No hay nada como sentir que quieren a tu hijo y sacan tiempo para ellos y todavía le falta!! Ella celebra una semana entera! 😂
Beyond blessed! Goodnight 🫶
